1
00:00:32,920 --> 00:00:34,920
What the hell do you think you’re doing, Chat?!

2
00:00:37,340 --> 00:00:38,448
Do my job.

3
00:00:40,110 --> 00:00:42,584
You humiliated me right in front of the board!

4
00:00:43,220 --> 00:00:45,176
What the hell is wrong with you?

5
00:00:46,080 --> 00:00:49,712
I've endured watching you feeding off my mother’s company for decades.

6
00:00:51,560 --> 00:00:53,224
This is enough, Dad.

7
00:00:53,870 --> 00:00:57,744
I’ve spent over ten years growing this company in your mother's place.

8
00:00:58,300 --> 00:01:01,240
And you’re saying I’ve been "feeding" off it?

9
00:01:02,856 --> 00:01:03,992
You ungrateful brat!

10
00:01:04,780 --> 00:01:08,968
Don’t you think I don’t know what you’ve been doing to this company, Dad.

11
00:01:16,700 --> 00:01:19,144
I didn’t raise you to be like this, Chat!

12
00:01:20,740 --> 00:01:24,368
You’re right, Mom is the one who raised me.

13
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:26,632
Not you.

14
00:01:37,180 --> 00:01:37,880
What is this?

15
00:01:44,460 --> 00:01:47,896
"Letter of Resignation from the Position of Company President"?

16
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:49,872
What is the meaning of this?

17
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:52,552
I’ve already handled everything.

18
00:01:53,090 --> 00:01:54,392
All you need to do is sign at the bottom of the letter.

19
00:01:55,420 --> 00:01:56,432
Pimchat!

20
00:01:57,900 --> 00:01:59,200
Come back here and finish this matter!

21
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:01,328
What else  to talk about, Dad?

22
00:02:02,410 --> 00:02:06,320
Is it about how you bought out every board member's shares immediately after Mom died?

23
00:02:07,180 --> 00:02:11,288
Or how you shipped me off to a foreign country just so you could appoint yourself President?

24
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:13,728
I’ve put up with enough, Dad.

25
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:18,624
I won't stand by and watch you destroy Mom’s company any longer.

26
00:02:51,180 --> 00:02:52,344
Look at that grin!

27
00:02:52,384 --> 00:02:54,112
What, is your girlfriend coming to pick you up?

28
00:02:54,550 --> 00:02:55,360
Shut up!

29
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:58,152
What girlfriend? That's not my girlfriend.

30
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:00,624
Well... You say she's not your girlfriend,

31
00:03:00,664 --> 00:03:02,620
but you’ve been beaming since we were in the class room.

32
00:03:03,704 --> 00:03:04,752
You're just talking nonsense.

33
00:03:29,640 --> 00:03:30,952
Oh, look! There she is.

34
00:03:31,350 --> 00:03:32,584
The "not-girlfriend" is here.

35
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:36,608
That’s enough. I’m leaving!

36
00:03:36,744 --> 00:03:38,610
Yeah, yeah, sure.

37
00:03:39,660 --> 00:03:41,144
Take good care of Ranya for us, okay,

38
00:03:41,550 --> 00:03:42,768
"Not-Girlfriend"?

39
00:04:19,750 --> 00:04:21,408
I missed you so much, P'Chat.

40
00:04:22,340 --> 00:04:23,376
I’ve been back for a while now.

41
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:24,980
It’s not like we just saw each other for the first time.

42
00:04:25,710 --> 00:04:28,600
But you were abroad for so long! ‘

43
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:31,040
Of course I missed you.

44
00:04:36,310 --> 00:04:37,336
What are you doing?

45
00:05:13,696 --> 00:05:15,120
Just sit still.

46
00:05:15,810 --> 00:05:17,416
But it’s my birthday today!

47
00:05:18,688 --> 00:05:20,690
Don't you have a present for me, P'Chat?

48
00:05:22,890 --> 00:05:24,464
You’ll surely get a gift,

49
00:05:25,140 --> 00:05:26,888
but you have to be a good girl first.

50
00:05:40,250 --> 00:05:41,976
I still can't open my eyes?

51
00:05:42,232 --> 00:05:43,584
Not yet.

52
00:05:45,180 --> 00:05:47,480
Don't let me catch you teasing me!

53
00:05:48,580 --> 00:05:50,240
How could I ever tease you?

54
00:05:54,150 --> 00:05:55,648
Okay... try opening your eyes now.

55
00:06:24,820 --> 00:06:26,232
Happy Birthday!

56
00:06:27,580 --> 00:06:30,680
P’Chat, this is…

57
00:06:34,510 --> 00:06:36,096
I have something I want to tell you, Ran.

58
00:06:36,540 --> 00:06:37,336
Yes?

59
00:06:59,416 --> 00:07:00,832
Ran, will you be my girlfriend?

60
00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:13,712
I’ve been waiting for you for so long.

61
00:07:15,820 --> 00:07:17,736
Well, you don’t have to wait anymore.

62
00:07:32,140 --> 00:07:34,936
P’Chat, could you put it on for me?

63
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:38,920
Of course. Come here, let me put it on for you.

64
00:08:02,656 --> 00:08:03,712
Does it look beautiful?

65
00:08:09,940 --> 00:08:11,216
You look the most beautiful.

66
00:08:52,230 --> 00:08:53,848
It’s still too soon.

67
00:08:54,736 --> 00:08:55,456
P’Chat...

68
00:09:08,352 --> 00:09:09,872
Ran, can you put it on for me too?

69
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:02,416
It’s still too soon.

70
00:10:03,650 --> 00:10:06,704
Oh, so you’re getting back at me? Hmm?

71
00:10:06,980 --> 00:10:08,264
Well, you started it first, P’Chat.

72
00:10:09,610 --> 00:10:11,408
I could just squeeze you!

73
00:10:11,448 --> 00:10:13,410
What a handful!

74
00:10:15,608 --> 00:10:16,640
Thank you.

75
00:10:17,180 --> 00:10:18,440
That’s okay.

76
00:10:18,980 --> 00:10:21,184
For you, I’d give everything.

77
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:33,840
Wait, you said it was too soon?

78
00:10:34,584 --> 00:10:36,040
It was just a touch... like this.

79
00:10:38,112 --> 00:10:39,272
Be careful.

80
00:10:41,530 --> 00:10:43,032
Happy Birthday.

81
00:10:43,330 --> 00:10:45,752
I love you most in the world, P’Chat.

82
00:10:46,940 --> 00:10:48,360
I love you too, Ran.
